data.description: Nice 2 Bedroom Block Home with Family Room off Dining Room separated by Glass Sliding Doors. 1 and 1/2 Bath. Utility Room with Washer/Dryer Hookup. Ceramic Tile Floors All Rooms!  Double Car Garage! New Garage Door w/ Remote Opener!  Large Fenced Rear Yard!  Covered Patio W/Paddle Fan! Exterior Clam Shell Awnings covering all large Windows!  Recently Painted Interior and Exterior!  New Double Door Refrigerator!   New Dropin Glass Stove Top!  New Double Stacked Oven!  Comfortable front porch. New Kitchen Counter Tops and Double Sink!  New Bathroom Vanity and Light Fixture!  All New Doors in Whole House! New Levelor Verticals Blinds on Most Windows! City Water!  Great Location in Lake Marie Estates.  Easy access to Stores, Restaurants, Schools, Major Highways. St. John River with Boat Access minutes away.  This Home needs some TLC but is Great Location and Excellent Potential!  Septic System!  Bonus Room!   EASY PURCHASE FOR VETERAN BUYER!  SELLER WILL HELP WITH CLOSING COSTS!
